  "title": "Events Marketing Crew",
  "description": "<p>🌟Events Marketing Crew Member!!!🌟</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description:</p><p>We are looking for reliable and outgoing individuals to join our Events Marketing Crew. In this role, you will help promote our brand at various events, engage with attendees, and support on-site event operations. You should enjoy interacting with people, working in a fast-paced environment, and representing the company in a positive and professional manner.</p><p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Answer basic questions about the brand and direct attendees to more information</li><li>Collect customer information or feedback when required</li><li>Support the events team with general tasks throughout the event</li><li>Maintain a clean, organised, and visually appealing event space</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Strong communication and people skills</li><li>Friendly, enthusiastic, and proactive attitude</li><li>Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends</li><li>Able to lift and carry light equipment</li><li>Reliable and punctual</li></ul>",
